Hottest Communities are generated by an equation over its Comments, Likes and Shares
Hottest Posts are generated by an equation over its Comments, Likes and Shares

Hottest Communities metrics are evaulated within a fixed timebox
Hottest Posts metrics are evaulated within a fixed timebox

The Hottest Community is based on Likes			"and comments and shares"
The Hottest Post is based on Likes			"and comments and shares"

Hottest Community ranking is based on Comments and Likes							and shares
Hottest Post ranking is based on Comments and Likes							and shares

Hottest Community is based on User's interaction
Hottest Post is based on User's interaction

